{"tid":755820,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解金鐘站d矮肥啊嬸咁撚好撞","createTime":"2018-07-25T13:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T15:11:17.000Z","uid":71568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"73907f006be26b06d03bbcbc6087441eb2127f9f","tid":755820,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:25:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱繁忙時間望住個背心大隻仔本身逼左係車箱門口最邊邊既位 笑笑口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知身邊突然閃出個矮肥婆，成粒波咁撞入去嘗試塞自己入架車到，撞撚到個大隻仔縮曬肚咁先夠位比條肥婆企，個樣仲&ldquo;拿&quot; 埋一舊好痛苦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下架車到我上，我本身好地地又係企係車邊。但係又有條仆街矮肥婆，150都唔知有冇，pump我入車箱，我想比阻力但係發現車箱太逼根本好難發力站穩陣腳，比人由門口一路pump到車箱中間條紅柱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底點解佢地咁撚好撞??重心低?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身份人都叫做開運動唔細份 個大隻仔直頭健身教練咁既款都係比人sm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後七人欖球唔撚洗請外援啦搵班矮肥婆去玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bdc5bccaeebce881dc80578b99a9fffe8e69a9","tid":755820,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"483799c46e2913103fc4ff5bddf79f0d1383b571","tid":755820,"uid":71568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03bdc5bccaeebce881dc80578b99a9fffe8e69a9","tid":755820,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"屌你已經試過好撚多次 永遠塞完一輪settle曬每個人既企位之後總有d肥婆格硬擠下擠下擠入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地仲要好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb71372bdc7fc113eeb5462a0c87c4e8b4d366c","tid"